schools.name: Youree Dr. Middle Advanced Placement Magnet School

data.description: Back On The Market! Welcome to this charming brick home nestled in a highly sought-after neighborhood with an excellent school district. This property is conveniently located just minutes away from a variety of shopping and dining options. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the beautiful new floors that extend throughout the home, providing a fresh and modern feel. The walls have been tastefully painted with updated, contemporary colors, complemented by stylish lighting fixtures that illuminate each room. The kitchen is a true highlight, boasting a modern design with sleek granite countertops that provide ample space for meal preparation and entertaining. The updated bathrooms feature contemporary fixtures and finishes, creating a spa-like atmosphere for relaxation! Also for formal gatherings or intimate family meals, the home offers a lovely formal dining area complete with a cozy fireplace. The property also includes a convenient two-car attached carport!
